96
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,470
As we all know,

97
00:04:56,490 --> 00:04:58,770
our young generations, after growing up,

98
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,880
have gradually left their homes

99
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:02,230
