105
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:14,390
I hope you parents

106
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:16,340
can spread the word about our policies.

107
00:05:16,670 --> 00:05:18,670
We'd like to have them back

108
00:05:18,670 --> 00:05:20,340
to restore our glory.

109
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,770
Great!

110
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:22,870
Mayor Gu,

111
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,510
I'll be the first to respond to your call.

112
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:26,670
Later, I'll ask my son to come back.

113
00:05:26,670 --> 00:05:28,330
Chen Bo's son has been

114
