119
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:37,070
Yes, yes.

120
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:38,610
That's not necessary.

121
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,500
As their parents, you just need

122
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:42,150
to inform them about the policies.

123
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:43,350
If they're willing to come back,

124
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,600
we certainly welcome them.

125
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:46,680
But if they have any opinions or suggestions

126
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,860
about our policies,

127
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,830
they can come to me and talk with me directly.

128
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:52,690
We're willing to make changes.

129
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:54,470
I hope

130
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,940
those children will come back

131
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:57,920
not because their parents force them to,

132
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,310
but because they're attracted by the bright future

133
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:01,590
of Flower Street.

134
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:03,260
Only in this way

135
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:05,560
will they have the enthusiasm and motivation

136
00:06:05,590 --> 00:06:07,710
to make Flower Street better.

137
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:08,560
-Great. 
-That's right.

138
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:10,100
Mayor Gu makes a great point.

139
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:11,350
Anyway, no matter what,

140
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:14,670
today I've truly felt that

141
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,030
the Grand Canal

142
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,500
is a miracle.

143
00:06:17,970 --> 00:06:19,760
We should all take pride in it.

144
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:22,160
Then let's have another toast to this miracle.

145
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:23,790
Come on.

146
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,790
Cheers.

