203
00:08:26,290 --> 00:08:27,210
Your words should carry weight.

204
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,160
He Shen?

205
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:31,340
I-I didn't say that. Y-You're

206
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,970
more like Li Hongzhang in the company.

207
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,250
Is that a compliment or an insult?

208
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,070
A compliment!

209
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,600
Minister Li was a renowned statesman of his time.

210
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:39,620
He contributed greatly to prolonging the Qing dynasty.

211
00:08:39,650 --> 00:08:40,580
Knock it off.

212
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,799
Alright, I'll ask about it.

213
00:08:44,179 --> 00:08:46,440
If it works with the schedule, we'll go back together.

214
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,290
Great, Minister Xie!

