00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,980
Cheers.

227
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:12,940
I'm leaving.

228
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:13,430
Take care.

229
00:09:13,430 --> 00:09:14,350
Don't stay out late. Bye-bye.

230
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,530
Let me know when you're home.

231
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,540
Bye-bye.

232
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:19,910
I'm heading off too.

233
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,470
I'll walk home. See you tomorrow.

234
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,380
Watch out for cars.

235
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:23,550
Be careful.

236
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,650
Let's go. You can stay over at my place tonight.

237
00:09:29,930 --> 00:09:31,080
