241
00:09:38,330 --> 00:09:39,250
Management.

242
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:42,500
I didn't have experience before,

243
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,060
but after running around for a while recently,

244
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:47,390
I think I'm ready.

245
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:49,350
Well,

246
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:51,970
